reviewText: My son is very pleased with this DVD.
I love this movie ! I watch all the time , it brings such good childhood memories  I recommend everyone to buy it for their kids or even themselves (: it's very educational and fun to watch

I remembered watching this show as a teen while babysitting and so I bought it for my daughter who just loves it. Its a very sweet show with a lot of good growing up lessons but its generally not heavy handed about it. The puppets are Henson-esque and don't come of creepy or scary at all. Recommended.

Wimzie's House: A World of Enchantment  Fun adventures with lessons for young children with the adorable fuzzy monsters in Wimzie's pre-school day-care world.  The games and stories, songs and activities will be fun for your child to follow along with these lovable monsters who are teaching as they create fun
